7. Notifications → “Whispers, Not Alarms”
Description (exactly as presented earlier):
No spammy emails. No robotic alerts.



Instead:

“Your vehicle’s risk profile just shifted.”

“New insight available.”

“A component you asked about just became cheaper.”


This makes the system feel alive but not needy.

Code (paste as-is into Netlify as index.html for Section 7):

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>VINvoyant — Whispers, Not Alarms</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#05060a; --ink:#eaf0ff; --muted:rgba(234,240,255,.72);
      --stroke:rgba(234,240,255,.14);
      --accent:#7c5cff; --accent2:#00d4ff; --ok:#24ff7a; --bad:#ff2e6a;
      --shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
      --radius: 22px;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html,body{height:100%}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial;
      color:var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(1200px 700px at 50% 20%, rgba(0,212,255,.14), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(900px 600px at 20% 80%, rgba(124,92,255,.16), transparent 60%),
        var(--bg);
      overflow-x:hidden;
    }

    .wrap{min-height:100%; display:grid; place-items:center; padding:28px 16px}
    .card{
      width:min(1100px, 100%);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      border:1px solid var(--stroke);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20,24,35,.82), rgba(10,12,18,.82));
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
      position:relative;
    }
    .card::before{
      content:""; position:absolute; inset:-2px;
      background: radial-gradient(700px 300px at 15% 15%, rgba(0,212,255,.22), transparent 60%),
                  radial-gradient(700px 300px at 85% 85%, rgba(124,92,255,.20), transparent 60%);
      opacity:.8; pointer-events:none;
    }
    .inner{position:relative; padding: 22px}
    .h{margin:0 0 6px; font-size: 28px}
    .p{margin:0 0 18px; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.5; font-size: 14px}

    .grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr .9fr;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items:start;
    }
    @media (max-width: 980px){ .grid{grid-template-columns:1fr} }

    .panel{
      border-radius: 18px;
      border:1px solid rgba(234,240,255,.10);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.25);
      padding: 16px;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .panelTitle{
      margin:0 0 10px;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing:.04em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: rgba(234,240,255,.80);
    }

    /* Whisper feed */
    .feed{display:grid; gap:10px}
    .whisper{
      border-radius: 16px;
      border:1px solid rgba(234,240,255,.10);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.25);
      padding: 12px;
      display:grid;
      gap: 6px;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
      transform: translateY(10px);
      opacity: 0;
      animation: arrive .45s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1) forwards;
    }
    @keyframes arrive{
      to{transform: translateY(0px); opacity: 1;}
    }
    .whisper::after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute; inset:0;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(0,212,255,.14), transparent);
      transform: translateX(-120%);
      animation: shimmer 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
      opacity:.6;
      pointer-events:none;
    }
    @keyframes shimmer{
      0%{transform:translateX(-120%)}
      55%{transform:translateX(120%)}
      100%{transform:translateX(120%)}
    }

    .wTop{display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px}
    .wTitle{font-weight: 950; letter-spacing:.02em}
    .wTime{color: rgba(234,240,255,.66); font-size: 12px}
    .wBody{color: rgba(234,240,255,.80); font-size: 13px; line-height:1.45}

    /* Quiet intensity indicator */
    .tone{
      display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .pill{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:8px;
      padding: 8px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border:1px solid rgba(234,240,255,.16);
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.35);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing:.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 11px;
      user-select:none;
    }
    .pill.ok{border-color: rgba(36,255,122,.35); color: rgba(36,255,122,.92)}
    .pill.info{border-color: rgba(0,212,255,.35); color: rgba(0,212,255,.92)}
    .pill.calm{border-color: rgba(124,92,255,.35); color: rgba(124,92,255,.92)}

    .actions{margin-top: 12px; display:flex; gap:10px; justify-content:flex-end; flex-wrap:wrap}
    .btn{
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border:1px solid rgba(234,240,255,.16);
      cursor:pointer;
      font-weight: 950;
      letter-spacing:.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.30);
      color: rgba(234,240,255,.92);
      transition: transform .16s ease, filter .16s ease;
    }
    .btn.primary{
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124,92,255,.95), rgba(0,212,255,.72));
      color: #05060a;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(0,212,255,.10);
    }
    .btn:hover{transform: translateY(-2px); filter: brightness(1.08)}
    .btn:active{transform: translateY(0px); filter: brightness(.98)}

    /* Bossy whisper overlay (commanding but not spammy) */
    .overlay{
      position:fixed; inset:0;
      display:none; place-items:center;
      background: rgba(0,0,0,.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
