8. Emotional Layer → “You Are Being Taken Care Of”
Description (exactly as presented earlier):
This is the invisible billion-dollar layer.



Tone:

Calm

Assured

Curious

Never panicked

Never salesy


The interface speaks like a great doctor or a great pilot:
Not dramatic. Not casual. Competent.

This is what people trust with expensive things.

Code (paste as-is into Netlify as index.html for Section 8):

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>VINvoyant — You Are Being Taken Care Of</title>
  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#05060a; --ink:#eaf0ff; --muted:rgba(234,240,255,.72);
      --stroke:rgba(234,240,255,.14);
      --accent:#7c5cff; --accent2:#00d4ff; --ok:#24ff7a;
      --shadow: 0 30px 90px rgba(0,0,0,.6);
      --radius: 22px;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html,body{height:100%}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial;
      color:var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(1200px 700px at 50% 20%, rgba(124,92,255,.18), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(900px 500px at 80% 70%, rgba(0,212,255,.12), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(900px 600px at 20% 80%, rgba(36,255,122,.08), transparent 60%),
        var(--bg);
      overflow-x:hidden;
    }

    .wrap{
      min-height:100%;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      padding:28px 16px;
      position:relative;
    }

    /* Calm, assured “field” */
    .field{
      position:absolute; inset:-60px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(700px 380px at 50% 30%, rgba(0,212,255,.12), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(700px 380px at 50% 70%, rgba(124,92,255,.14), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(900px 700px at 50% 55%, rgba(0,0,0,.65), rgba(0,0,0,.92));
      animation: drift 10s ease-in-out infinite;
      opacity:.9;
      pointer-events:none;
    }
    @keyframes drift{
      0%,100%{transform: scale(1) rotate(0deg)}
      50%{transform: scale(1.03) rotate(1deg)}
    }

    .card{
      width:min(980px, 100%);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      border:1px solid var(--stroke);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20,24,35,.82), rgba(10,12,18,.82));
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
      position:relative;
    }
    .card::before{
      content:""; position:absolute; inset:-2px;
      background: radial-gradient(700px 300px at 15% 15%, rgba(124,92,255,.30), transparent 60%),
